From 79fda5873a6ff9bfd67dea1bc2527c9cf99d3d31 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Ryan X. Charles" <ryan@ryanxcharles.com>
Date: Fri, 29 May 2026 11:10:26 -0500
Subject: [PATCH 29/73] Expose PDF API surface

Two private keys stayed on the ring,
Chrome's common map began to sing.
The door still stuck, but now we know:
The renderer never asked the show.
---
